name: Storm #1002
description:
This image is part of a sequence that captures what feels to be a rather dark storm.  The animation reminds me of storm sequences often depicted in movies and television from the 60s and 70s.   

It was coded in GLSL.  

For now, please consider this image as a placeholder, not for sale.  Higher resolution versions will be uploaded in the coming days as I learn more about Hic et Nunc.
